    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that sounds like a plan. a bit nervous about the cream though, how many times a day should i be putting it on? and should i wrap it in a bandage or just leave it open to the air? i really want to make sure i do this right so i dont have to spend money on a doctor visit.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
