      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Apply the antibiotic cream three to four times a day, morning and night, making sure to clean the area first each time. Wrap it loosely with a sterile gauze bandage to keep it protected and keep the moisture in, which is key for healing. If you leave it open, you're inviting germs in, and you don't want that! Follow these steps precisely, and you'll be looking well in no time.",
      "source": "target",
